bnf: backup_manager = enabled => backup_compression_algorithm in {zlib, bzip2, zstd}
allow_availability_zone_fallback = true => scheduler_default_filters in {{ AvailabilityZoneFilter, OTHER_FILTERS }}
osapi_volume_extension != null => osapi_volume_ext_list is valid and non-null
backup_gcs_object_size = (backup_gcs_block_size * n) where n is an integer
